  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Cut your<strong> aubergine[s]</strong> in half lengthways (including the stalk), then score the flesh in a criss-cross pattern, taking care not to cut through to the skin</p><p>Rub the cut sides of the aubergine with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>scored aubergine halves</strong> to a baking tray, cut-side down, and put in the oven for 25-30 min or until the flesh is tender</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
