    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>tomato </strong>and <strong>shallot </strong>to the pan with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>diced</strong> <strong>chilli </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>and <strong>crushed garlic</strong> and cook for 5-7 min or until soft</p><p>Trim, then finely slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
