    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile,<strong> </strong>zest<strong> half </strong>your <strong>lime[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Roll the<strong> lime[s] </strong>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
