            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted aubergine </strong>over the <strong>basmati rice </strong>and top with the <strong>warm sambal sauce</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>spicy zesty nuts </strong>and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person and serve to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
